{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c1254b896b","title":"致电吊暗冯玉祥氏之夹","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"be4f7b50c7","index":0,"year":1948,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"c1254b896b"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"89c3aea95c","type":"paragraph","text":"致电吊暗冯玉祥氏之夹”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"},{"id":"23d3e688b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年9月7日）李济深先生并转中国国民党革命委员会诸先生鉴惊悉冯玉祥先生于归国途中不幸退难，不胜震停。冯先生连年为民主事业奔走呼号，此次归国，对于中国人民民主事业，定多贡截，今忽置此意外，实为国家民族之损失。特电致暗，并申宾思","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"},{"id":"325e2c54d1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"},{"id":"df1d0f69a1","type":"paragraph","text":"九月七日冯夫人李德全女士礼鉴惊悉冯玉祥先生及令媛不卷退难，至深痛惊。冯先生致力民主，功在国家。尚希勉抑衰思，并为实现冯先生遗志而奋斗","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"},{"id":"8d0f54dd22","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东朱德","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"},{"id":"b175fc335b","type":"paragraph","text":"九月七日[1]这是毛泽东和未德联名为冯玉样在同国参如新政协会议途中不幸因轮楚失火资世，给中国国民党革会委员会及码玉样夫人李德全女士的喧电。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b"}],"page":{"id":"597f70cb09","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"c1254b896b","start":447,"end":447}}}},"__N_SSG":true}